    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 PWM implementation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Design:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>One <ref refid="classStmPwm" kindref="compound">StmPwm</ref> per TIM_HandleTypeDef (one hardware timer).</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Channels 0–3 map to TIM_CHANNEL_1..TIM_CHANNEL_4.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Duty cycle sets the CCR register relative to ARR.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Frequency changes recalculate ARR+PSC (affects all channels on the timer).</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Complementary / dead-time support via TIM1/TIM8 BDTR register. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
